        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Kings 18:18",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and compare ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Isaiah 22:15-25",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The tribute - The marginal reading, \"levy,\" is preferable. The reference is to the forced laborers whom Solomon employed in his great works (marginal reference). ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "The tribute - The marginal reading, \"levy,\" is preferable. The reference is to the forced laborers whom Solomon employed in his great works (marginal reference). ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
